title: SSG Keygen Adobe CS2 Illustrator Photoshop GoLive InDesign Creat
description:
This is the official SSG keygen for:

- Creative Suite 2 Premium Edition
- Creative Suite 2 Standard Edition
- Photoshop CS2 9.0
- Illustrator CS2 12.0
- InDesign CS2 4.0
- GoLive CS2 8.0
- Version Cue CS2 2.0
- Acrobat 7.0 Professional

This Keygen provides the serial number and telephone activation code for any of the pieces of software from a drop-down box.  I can personally vouch for the fact that it works for Photoshop and Illustrator.
